    <briefdescription>
<para>Weighted-Jacobi smoother for AlgVector/SpMatrix linear systems. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Encapsulates a configurable number of damped Jacobi sweeps that operate on the diagonal extracted from a supplied sparse matrix. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
